  rdfs:comment           "Direct binding was confirmed by pull-down experiments with recombinantly expressed proteins (Fig. S1B)." , "Worms expressing only GFP::SYD-2 (Fig. 1E) exhibit a fluorescence lifetime of 2.74 ns ± 0.01 (n = 11 worms), typical for GFP in the absence of FRET and significantly higher than in worms expressing both GFP::SYD-2 and UNC-104::mRFP (Fig. 1D; color bar and lifetime histograms in Fig. 1F; also see SI text). " , "In addition to the previously published interactions, we found that either all (1–695) or some coiled-coils (341–695) of SYD-2 weakly interact with UNC-104 domain constructs (Fig. 1B and Fig. S1).X" ;
